Class PatientMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bch.c3pro.consumer.model.PatientMap

  • @Entity
public class PatientMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity model for db table patient_map. It captures the link between the signature generated by the iOS system and the subject id generated for i2b2.

    CHIP-IHL
